---
---
<section id="about" class="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container about-inner">

    <div class="about-photo reveal">
      <img
        src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/?$/, '/')}founder.jpg`}
        alt="Donna O'Brien, founder of OB Senior Concierge"
        width="400"
        height="500"
        loading="lazy"
        class="founder-photo"
      />
      <div class="about-credential">
        <div class="credential-line"></div>
        <p class="credential-name">Donna O'Brien</p>
        <p class="credential-title">Founder, OB Senior Concierge</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <p class="section-label">About Us</p>
      <h2 id="about-heading">A Personal Approach to Senior Support</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <!--
        TODO: Donna — please personalize the paragraph below with your own story.
        Suggested elements to include:
          - Your background (what you did before, any relevant experience)
          - What motivated you to start OB Senior Concierge
          - Your personal connection to San Diego / North County
          - Your commitment to the client relationship (one-on-one, consistent)
        Keep the tone warm and personal — this is where clients decide if they trust you.
      -->
      <p>
        OB Senior Concierge was founded on a simple belief: every older adult deserves
        attentive, consistent, and genuinely caring support — delivered by someone who
        takes the time to understand how they live and what matters most to them.
      </p>
      <p>
        With deep roots in San Diego's North County, I bring a commitment to
        discretion, reliability, and a truly personal relationship. You won't be
        passed between staff or handed a roster of strangers. You get one dependable
        point of contact — someone who shows up, follows through, and treats your
        home and routines with the respect they deserve.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're looking for a little help with the administrative side of life,
        or a consistent presence that gives your family peace of mind, I'm here to
        make things easier — quietly, capably, and always on your terms.
      </p>

      <div class="about-values">
        <div class="value">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="9" stroke="#8aa090" stroke-width="1.25"/>
            <path d="M6 10l3 3 5-5" stroke="#8aa090" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Personally delivered — always</span>
        </div>
        <div class="value">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="9" stroke="#8aa090" stroke-width="1.25"/>
            <path d="M6 10l3 3 5-5" stroke="#8aa090" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Discreet &amp; trustworthy</span>
        </div>
        <div class="value">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="9" stroke="#8aa090" stroke-width="1.25"/>
            <path d="M6 10l3 3 5-5" stroke="#8aa090" stroke-width="1.25" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Serving North County San Diego</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Let's Connect</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 340px 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Photo */
  .about-photo {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .founder-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgb(138 160 144 / 0.15), rgb(31 58 82 / 0.08));
    border: 1px dashed rgb(138 160 144 / 0.4);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .placeholder-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--sage);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .about-credential { padding-left: 0.25rem; }

  .credential-line {
    width: 2rem;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .credential-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 600;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .credential-title {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: none;
  }

  /* Text */
  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .about-values {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--sage);
    margin-block: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-photo {
      max-width: 320px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
